data.text:
Claudia Jordan is 51 years and 4 month(s) old. She was born in 12 Apr, 1973. Claudia Angela Jordan is an actress, model, businesswoman, and reality television and radio personality from the United States. She is best known for modeling on the American versions of Deal or No Deal, and The Price Is Right and competing on Celebrity Apprentice seasons 2 and 6. Jordan appeared in the seventh season of Bravo's reality show The Real Housewives of Atlanta.
